apiResult.english: I am Lelouch Vi Britannia, son of the late Empress Marianne. The prince abandoned by his empire. If there are any that think they can go beyond my despair, then let them try.
apiResult.indo: Saya Lelouch Vi Britannia, putra mendiang Permaisuri Marianne. Pangeran ditinggalkan oleh kerajaannya. Jika ada yang berpikir mereka bisa melampaui keputusasaanku, biarkan mereka mencobanya.
apiResult.anime: Code Geass: Lelouch of the Rebellion
